      "role": "user",
      "content": "but what a counselor is gonna say? that i should just keep doing this? just keep waking up to an empty bed and eating meals for one and pretending it's okay? it doesn't feel like \"moving forward.\" it feels like I'm just dragging a corpse around. it's just so exhausting. everything is so pointless without him.",
